HOST KV PUT ABI: host_kv_put returns 1 on success, 0 on failure (non-POSIX). All wasm crates must check rc!=0 for Ok. Three callers had inverted checks (rs-plugkit wasm_dispatch.rs:584 close(), rs-exec wasm_host.rs:57, rs-learn wasm_host.rs:69) - fixed 2026-06-19. Silent data loss and task lifecycle corruption on every write until fixed.